        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent. | Railway Station | Orpington. S.E.R.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Jan 14<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> / 79</date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I must send you a line to thank you for your letter. The notion of the girl those men &amp; women are descended from distinct progenitors is certainly a very ludicrous one.<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p>
<p>Dear Sir | Yours faithfully | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
            
